<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>20</hymn_number>
<author>Landy RABENIRAINY</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Nosy ô! mihainoa,
 Atongilano ny sofinareo,
 Ry lavitra fihaviana,
 O! Mihainoa ianareo.
 Izaho no hiady ho anao,
 Ho Famonjena ho anao,
 Koa matokia ianao,
 Ekeo ho fanavotana anao.
 Moa tsy fiadanana sy fahasambarana,
 No katsahinao ety, hilofosanao ery,
 Andrandrao ny masonao,
 Ka henoy izao teny izao :
 &quot;Raiso Jeso ho anao&quot;.</lyrics>
<title>MIHAINOA RY NOSY ASAFA20</title>
</song>